M|The |From|
M|The |**St|** bd a research stack of top 10 buying signals — 5 company triggers, 5 person triggers. Stack-rank by relevance.
M|The |**St|** bd a 3x3 template: (1) personalization attached to a problem, (2) problem you solve, (3) one-sentence solution + lo-friction CTA.
M|The |**St|** cr 5 "trigger templates" — pre-written personalization paragraphs for each trigger, w/ a smooth segue into the problem.
M|The |tx|The personalization must logically connect to the problem. This creates 5 reusable triggers w/ the rest of the em constant. A top SDR writes a personalized em in **under 3 minutes**.
M|The |it|**Demographic** — Age, profession, background
M|The |it|**Technographic** — Tech stack, tools used
M|The |it|**Firmographic** — Company size, funding, industry, growth stage
M|The |it|**Psychographic** — Values, passions, beliefs (highest-impact dimension)
M|The |tx|Tapping into what prospects are passionate abt drives significantly higher rp rates.
